    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in good condition. The exterior shows minor wear consistent with normal use, with no significant dents, rust, or damage. The interior is clean and functional, with moderate wear on high-contact surfaces such as the driver's seat and door panels. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been maintained. A solid, reliable vehicle with no major issues.",
